    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. The dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, ensuring precise variable valve timing and peak torque delivery. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, and the suspension geometry is sharpened with polyurethane bushings. While the Titanium Silver finish shows minor road rash and typical patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are exceptional, featuring a cooling system refresh and recent valve adjustment. It is a mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
