    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances daily utility with a premium feel. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a high-gloss shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the seats are firm and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats, and all interior electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in solid health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's interval schedule, with a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection completed just last month. The brakes are responsive, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been primarily garage-kept. It represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car without the 'new car' price tag. Full service records are available for review.",
